{"tid":2115393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔講政見，熱血公民個陳到(敬業sir)算唔算係男人之恥？","createTime":"2020-07-19T13:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T15:07:19.000Z","uid":73381,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"194a2eba38f6b729d816f820b7fdbc384e495b87","tid":2115393,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nMZUA9PQ-pU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnMZUA9PQ-pU&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8prktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=6ddc6897\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nMZUA9PQ-pU</a><br />\n<br />\n平時網上講野就兇狠 屌哂全世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老味做節目嗰陣對住何洋達(大上)就成隻狗咁撚樣 比人屌到仆街都淨係識係到汪汪汪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己做節目要自己課金已經柒到仆街 仲要課得嗰廿蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地黃逃健(健仔)同王頴思(王姑娘)做社區主任做到依家變埋區議員<br />\n呢條撚屌就做到收哂皮 到依家都仲係係網上鳩屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/153541_139aca230c79764a559448aecb989fa8.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F153541_139aca230c79764a559448aecb989fa8.PNG&h=7a900989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc057b42e4b602535a30ff61483c9cede7d2547c","tid":2115393,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\